{"ID":"20250709165450-pyk98bl","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250709165450-pyk98bl","title":"DROID-SLAM","type":"doc","updated":"20250709170102"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250709165450-h3htowv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709165450-h3htowv","updated":"20250709165528"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"DROID-SLAM是一种用于食品中运动估计与三维重建的深度学习方法。"}]},{"ID":"20250709165532-m4lq8e1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709165532-m4lq8e1","updated":"20250709165630"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Bundle Adjustment（BA）光束平差法，在多视图集合中，用于同时优化相机位姿和三维点的一种技术"}]},{"ID":"20250709165631-mcm33wg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709165631-mcm33wg","updated":"20250709165716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可微光束平差层：是指这个BA过程被设计成可导的，可以嵌入神经网络中进行端到端的训练。"}]},{"ID":"20250709165717-z21p015","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709165717-z21p015","updated":"20250709170102"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong mark","TextMarkTextContent":"隐式调整不确定性模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"  ：不是直接去建模或者手工设定特征的不确定性，而是通过神经网络和训练过程，间接学习出不确定性的表达方式。采用了简化后的对角协方差模型进行光束平差，（各个维度之间没有相关性，只有各自的方差），牺牲了表达能力，换来计算上的简便。"}]},{"ID":"20250709165857-m2vv8hk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250709165857-m2vv8hk","updated":"20250709165857"}}]}